WEBVTT

00:01.917 --> 00:04.248
<i>Kids, sometimes when</i>
<i>you're about to give up</i>

00:04.250 --> 00:06.763
<i>on your love life forever</i>
<i>for the 17th time,</i>

00:07.172 --> 00:09.156
<i>destiny intervenes.</i>

00:09.489 --> 00:12.740
<i>Instead of rushing in,</i>
<i>I took my time</i>

00:12.742 --> 00:14.458
<i>to think up the perfect</i>
<i>opening line.</i>

00:16.329 --> 00:17.912
Wait, no, damn it,
come back! You're really...

00:17.914 --> 00:19.998
You're pretty!

00:20.000 --> 00:21.249
And before I could call
out after her,

00:21.251 --> 00:22.617
in any kind of embarrassing way

00:22.619 --> 00:24.836
that a bunch of teenagers made
fun of for the next five stops

00:24.838 --> 00:26.804
while I stared straight ahead
and pretended not to hear them,

00:26.806 --> 00:28.056
she was gone.

00:28.058 --> 00:31.225
But here's the thing
about Ted Mosby:

00:31.227 --> 00:32.476
he doesn't give up.

00:32.479 --> 00:34.128
Stalker Ted alert.

00:34.130 --> 00:35.563
Repeat, Stalker
Ted alert.

00:35.565 --> 00:37.649
Already has a yellow
legal pad going.

00:37.651 --> 00:39.767
Repeat, already has
a yellow legal pad going.

00:39.769 --> 00:41.235
I'm not stalking.

00:41.237 --> 00:42.987
I just jotted down
a few details

00:42.989 --> 00:44.155
to help me find her.

00:44.157 --> 00:45.490
Uh, like the fact

00:45.492 --> 00:47.358
that her smile was cute,

00:47.360 --> 00:48.493
but a bit crooked,

00:48.495 --> 00:50.311
which can be a sign
of teeth grinding.

00:50.313 --> 00:51.996
So I called up
the city's

00:51.998 --> 00:53.247
top five TMJ specialists,

00:53.249 --> 00:55.667
and here's where it
gets interesting.

00:55.669 --> 00:57.168
Not interesting,
Ted, creepy.

00:57.170 --> 00:58.169
Let her go.

00:58.171 --> 00:59.320
No, this is destiny.

00:59.322 --> 01:01.673
No, Ted,
this is forcing it.

01:01.675 --> 01:05.009
When Lily and I met,
I mean, that was destiny.

01:05.010 --> 01:06.827
<i>She could've knocked</i>
<i>on any door</i>

01:06.829 --> 01:08.262
<i>to find someone</i>
<i>to fix her stereo,</i>

01:08.264 --> 01:09.681
<i>but she knocked on mine.</i>

01:13.268 --> 01:14.936
Now hand over
the pad.

01:17.506 --> 01:19.140
Ted...

01:20.008 --> 01:21.509
And the backup pad.

01:21.511 --> 01:23.611
<i>They were right.</i>

01:23.613 --> 01:25.446
<i>You can't force destiny.</i>

01:25.448 --> 01:27.014
<i>If it's gonna happen,</i>
<i>it's gonna happen.</i>

01:28.735 --> 01:30.234
<i>And funny story, kids...</i>

01:30.236 --> 01:31.869
Oh, my God.

01:31.871 --> 01:33.154
It's you.

01:33.156 --> 01:35.039
<i>...it happened.</i>

