03:08.807 --> 03:11.474
Like Lloyd Dobler holding
up the boom box

03:11.476 --> 03:13.643
outside Diane Court's window
in <i>Say Anything.</i>

03:13.645 --> 03:14.977
But if
one person

03:14.979 --> 03:16.112
isn't into the other,

03:16.114 --> 03:18.648
the same gesture comes off
serial-killer crazy,

03:18.650 --> 03:20.400
or Dahmer.

03:20.402 --> 03:21.784
Now, Marshall, the story of

03:21.786 --> 03:24.287
