05:51.302 --> 05:54.420
<i>P.S. I love you, you, you."</i>

05:54.422 --> 05:56.105
<i>This is "ridikilus."</i>

05:56.107 --> 05:58.224
<i>Who cares who she</i>
<i>was obsessed with?</i>

05:58.226 --> 06:01.594
<i>What, am I gonna go to Canada</i>
