06:05.650 --> 06:07.433
<i>to fixate on</i>
<i>one little detail.</i>

06:07.435 --> 06:09.201
That fire alarm--
did you pull it?

06:09.203 --> 06:10.536
Ugh...

06:10.538 --> 06:11.871
This is embarrassing.

06:11.873 --> 06:14.707
I wasn't gonna tell you this,
but...

06:14.709 --> 06:16.075
<i>I'd come so far,</i>

06:16.077 --> 06:18.711
<i>only to be sent packing</i>
<i>by that security guard,</i>

06:18.713 --> 06:20.463
<i>and... well...</i>

