10:11.340 --> 10:12.539
She set a fire, Ted!

10:12.541 --> 10:13.774
Dahmer.

10:13.776 --> 10:14.925
You're just jealous 'cause Lily

10:14.927 --> 10:16.093
never burned anything for you.

10:16.095 --> 10:17.811
Clearly you never
tried her pot roast.

10:18.914 --> 10:20.097
I actually brought this

10:20.099 --> 10:21.348
for something totally different,

10:21.350 --> 10:22.416
but it worked out, right?

10:22.418 --> 10:23.600
Okay, anyway,

10:23.602 --> 10:24.501
here's my thing.

10:24.503 --> 10:26.103
Ladies and gentlemen,

10:26.105 --> 10:28.138
I have in my back pocket

10:28.140 --> 10:29.857
the answer to the question

10:29.859 --> 10:32.459
"Who was Robin obsessed with?"

10:32.461 --> 10:34.395
Hang on tight.

