<i>and totally rad robot, no one</i>

10:53.382 --> 10:57.334
<i>symbolized the 1990s</i>
<i>in Canada like Robin Sparkles.</i>

10:57.336 --> 11:00.454
<i>But as we'd all learn one</i>
<i>heartbreaking Grey Cup Sunday,</i>

11:00.456 --> 11:03.057
<i>Canada's sweetheart</i>
<i>had a dark side.</i>

11:03.059 --> 11:04.808
I'll never forget that moment.

11:04.810 --> 11:07.261
A little piece of Canada
died that day.

11:07.263 --> 11:09.029
To see her
throw her life away like that...

11:11.199 --> 11:12.433
...it was heartbreaking.

11:12.435 --> 11:14.084
I am so happy right now.

11:14.086 --> 11:16.828
I want to see her throw
her life away so badly.

11:16.853 --> 11:17.777
Yeah.

11:17.778 --> 11:20.378
We're all terrible people--
turn it up.

